(90, 1, '2019-01-30 12:22:58', '2019-01-30 12:22:58', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Let us tell you more.<br></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>EXPERIENCE COUNTS</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>White Tree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux in 2016. Stephanie has 12 years experience as a HR Generalist working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups &amp; SME’s to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to SME’s and local businesses.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>During her time in HR, Stephanie has headed up a number of HR projects, worked closely with a variety of HR Systems and integrated extensively within businesses at both an Operational and Strategic level. She provides business Managers and the board with a comprehensive and professional HR service along with ensuring companies work within current employment legislation and to best practice standards.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '28-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-30 12:22:58', '2019-01-30 12:22:58', '', 28, 'http://whitetree.localhost/28-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
