li><li>Employee Handbook</li><li>Letters </li><li>Data Entry </li><li>Document Management </li><li>Recruitment Administration </li><li>Ad hoc HR Administration </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-07 11:20:13', '2019-03-07 11:20:13', '', 5, 'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/07/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(10, 1, '2019-03-07 11:22:35', '2019-03-07 11:22:35', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR are an innovative, dynamic and diligent HR Consultancy. We pride ourselves on being flexible, bespoke and reliable enabling us to deliver premium HR solutions that work for you and your business.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux. Stephanie is CIPD qualified and has 12 years experience working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups, SME’s to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to small local businesses. During her time in HR, Stephanie has headed up a number of HR projects, worked closely with a variety of HR Systems and integrated extensively within organisations at both an Operational and Strategic level. She provides Business Managers, Key Stakeholders and Executives with a comprehensive and professional HR service along with ensuring companies work within current employment legislation and to best practice standards. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2019-03-14 13:30:31', '2019-03-14 13:30:31', '', 0, 'http://whitetree.localhost/?page_id=10', -3, 'page', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2019-03-07 11:22:35', '2019-03-07 11:22:35', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux in 2016. Stephanie has 12 years experience as a HR Generalist working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups, SME’s to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to small local businesses. During her time in HR, Stephanie has headed up a number of HR projects, worked closely with a variety of HR Systems and integrated extensively within organisations at both an Operational and Strategic level. She provides Business Managers, Key Stakeholders and Executives with a comprehensive and professional HR service along with ensuring companies work within current employment legislation and to best practice standards. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-07 11:22:35', '2019-03-07 11:22:35', '', 10, 'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/07/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(12, 1, '2019-03-07 11:27:11', '2019-03-07 11:27:11', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please complete the contact form below and we will get back to you (Name, email&lt; Contact Number, Brief description of service required, Preffered method of contact </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Alternatively  you can email or call us at:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Email: enquires@whitetreehr.co.uk</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Phone: xxxxxx</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-07 11:27:11', '2019-03-07 11:27:11', '', 2, 'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/07/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(13, 1, '2019-03-07 11:29:12', '2019-03-07 11:29:12', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here at WhiteTree HR we pride ourselves on being diligent and innovative whilst creating bespoke solutions. We are perfectly positioned to collaborate with businesses on HR projects within their organisations, working with you from concept to completion. Whatever your requirements we are here to support your business. We can provide advice, guidance, reports, reviews or complete projects for you. Contact us today to discuss how we can help you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Create bespoke HR projects</li><li>Aid businesses in completion of\nprojects </li><li>Review existing projects, analyse\nand improve existing projects or compliment the development of ongoing projects\nwithin the business</li><li>Project integration </li><li>Project documentation </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Project HR', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'project-hr__trashed', '', '', '2019-03-14 10:58:13', '2019-03-14 10:58:13', '', 0, 'http://whitetree.localhost/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
